villasData.description:
Multistory apartment is available for sale. It has a carpet area of 507 sq-ft, and it is in a good location. Please contact for more details.

Property Specifications:

- Spacious flat with a carpet area of 507 sq. ft.
- Located on the 3rd floor of a 5-story building.
- Semi-furnished with well-crafted wardrobes.
- 1 bedroom, 2 bathrooms (one attached, one common).
- Modern modular kitchen with dedicated utility area.
- Vitrified flooring, south-facing, and Vastu compliant.

Facilities:

- Covered parking, 24-hour water supply, and power backup.
- Security guard and one lift for easy access.

Locality:

- Schools, hospitals, malls within 2 km.
- Public transport, railway, and metro 9-10 km away.
- Nearby banks and ATMs available.
